violence renewing in West Bank and Gaza, after Israeli Prime
Minister Benjamin Netanyahu gave orders in March to build
thousands of Jewish homes at a East Jerusalem hillside.
</P>
<P>
The Palestinians hold that the peace crisis was a result of
Israel's settlement building while Israel repeatedly charged that
Palestinian violence was the main obstacle to progress in
peace-making.
</P>
<P>
Egypt stepped in as a main mediator for peace between Israel
and Palestinians after the U.S., a key sponsor of the Mideast peace
talks, has lowered its mediation profile. 
