As the earlier phase was to deploy multi-national forces in the
troubled tiny Balkan nation to safeguard food relief operations,
the next should be devoted to help rebuild the country, he said.
</P>
<P>
In a related development, about 400 soldiers of the first
contingent of Italian servicemen pulling out from Albania have
come back to Italy today. 
</P>
</TEXT>
